---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About" description="Learn about TechHub - our mission, values, and purpose." pageType="about">
  <article class="policy-page">
    <h1>About TechHub</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        TechHub is an independent tech resource dedicated to providing practical developer tools, 
        quality technical content, and verified promotional offers. Our goal is to help developers 
        and tech enthusiasts find useful resources without wading through low-quality or misleading content.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Developer Tools:</strong> Practical utilities for working with Markdown, JSON, XML, and text comparison.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Articles:</strong> In-depth tutorials, guides, and reference material.</li>
        <li><strong>Tech News:</strong> Curated news with original analysis explaining why each story matters.</li>
        <li><strong>Verified Promotions:</strong> Researched referral programs and special offers from trusted providers.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> We verify information before publishing and update content when needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We clearly disclose relationships with partners and advertisers.</li>
        <li><strong>Usefulness:</strong> We focus on content that helps real users solve real problems.</li>
        <li><strong>Independence:</strong> We maintain editorial independence from promotional considerations.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Who Runs This Site</h2>
      <p>
        TechHub is a personal project created and maintained by xipeter. It's a space to share tools, 
        knowledge, and resources that I've found useful in my own work. This is not a company or 
        commercial enterprise—it's a personal website aimed at being genuinely useful.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions, suggestions, or want to report an issue? We'd love to hear from you. 
        Visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to get in touch.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .policy-page h1 { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); }
  .last-updated { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl); }
  .policy-page section { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl); }
  .policy-page h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md); color: var(--primary); }
  .policy-page ul { padding-left: var(--spacing-lg); }
  .policy-page li { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); }
  .policy-page a { color: var(--primary); }
</style>